sequenceDiagram
    actor User as User / RHOAI Component

    box rgb(232, 244, 253) Training Hub SDK
        participant Registry as Algorithm Registry
        participant Algo as Algorithm<br/>(SFT/OSFT/LoRA/GRPO/GEPA)
        participant Backend as Backend<br/>(pluggable)
    end

    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant vLLM as vLLM Server<br/>HTTP (configurable port)
    participant LLM as LLM Endpoint<br/>HTTPS via litellm
    participant FS as Local Filesystem
    participant Tracker as Experiment Tracker<br/>(W&B / MLflow / TB)

    Note over User,Tracker: Flow 1: SFT / OSFT Training

    User->>Registry: sft(model, data, output_dir, ...)<br/>or osft(model, data, ...)
    Registry->>Algo: Create algorithm + select backend
    Algo->>Backend: Validate params, configure backend
    Backend->>HF: Download model & tokenizer<br/>HTTPS/443, Token (optional)
    HF-->>Backend: Model artifacts
    Backend->>Backend: Launch torchrun subprocess<br/>TCP (master_port), cluster-internal
    Backend->>FS: Write checkpoints & metrics JSONL
    Backend-->>Algo: Training complete
    Algo-->>User: Output directory path

    opt Experiment Tracking Enabled
        Backend->>Tracker: Upload metrics<br/>HTTPS/443 (W&B) or HTTP (MLflow)
    end

    Note over User,Tracker: Flow 2: LoRA GRPO Training (ART Backend - Single GPU)

    User->>Registry: lora_grpo(model, dataset, reward_funcs, backend="art")
    Registry->>Algo: Create LoRAGRPOAlgorithm + ART backend
    Algo->>Backend: Serialize reward functions, prepare config
    Backend->>HF: Download base model<br/>HTTPS/443
    HF-->>Backend: Model artifacts
    Backend->>Backend: Create seed LoRA checkpoint<br/>(vLLM V1 compatibility)
    Backend->>Backend: Spawn ART subprocess

    loop GRPO Training Loop
        Backend->>vLLM: Generate rollouts<br/>HTTP (configurable port), API Key
        vLLM-->>Backend: Generated completions
        Backend->>Backend: Evaluate reward functions
        Backend->>Backend: Update model weights (LoRA)
    end

    Backend->>FS: Save LoRA adapter checkpoints
    Backend-->>User: Output directory path

    Note over User,Tracker: Flow 3: GRPO Training (verl Backend - Multi-GPU)

    User->>Registry: grpo(model, dataset, reward_funcs)
    Registry->>Algo: Create LoRAGRPOAlgorithm + verl backend
    Algo->>Backend: Generate Hydra config, serialize rewards to files
    Backend->>HF: Download base model<br/>HTTPS/443
    HF-->>Backend: Model artifacts
    Backend->>Backend: Spawn verl subprocess (Hydra)

    loop Distributed GRPO Training
        Backend->>Backend: FSDP distributed training<br/>NCCL/TCP (multi-GPU)
        Backend->>Backend: vLLM rollout workers (in-process)
        Backend->>Backend: Evaluate rewards (Dr. GRPO: token-level loss)
    end

    Backend->>FS: Save normalized LoRA checkpoints
    Backend-->>User: Output directory path

    Note over User,Tracker: Flow 4: GEPA Prompt Optimization

    User->>Registry: gepa(model, prompts, eval_fn, ...)
    Registry->>Algo: Create GEPAAlgorithm + backend
    Algo->>Backend: Configure evolutionary search

    loop Genetic-Pareto Optimization
        Backend->>LLM: Evaluate prompt candidates<br/>HTTPS via litellm, API Key
        LLM-->>Backend: Evaluation results
        Backend->>Backend: Selection, crossover, mutation
    end

    Backend->>FS: Save optimized prompts
    opt MLflow Backend
        Backend->>Tracker: Register optimized prompts<br/>HTTP (configurable)
    end
    Backend-->>User: Optimized prompts
